                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-115-off655 t18300415-115-crimeloc658"></join>. On the 30th of March the prisoner, who is my son-in-law, took away a suit of clothes and 16s. of mine; I found them at Bow-street - I had seen them three or four days before; I missed the money from a small box in the cupboard.</p>
